f I also need to adjust BCDSTU4145PrivateKey, but it seems like it only applies to inactive cases. Maybe I should update the test method name as well; that seems fine. Let’s ensure everything is set for the next steps!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_03a86127b9e34355016a25bdb080048194a5b95e949b07bc04\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqJb3ON27s_B6kjCOQLZkJiFkHQzdhzhs1-przku6uQ0enKI7ciJsCh-xKPCbOeFZ63sWVfI2zcxJdQSdS-qxPkGoNCaQxmWQgjJI-ElfT2T-5aUaq77esmxC6yoHhbPB8Jpb4kbrkCR1y2aiCNOCmIL1VFgqCus8-KNkl2peBdx66oc4Z7XSORLlR2XiXEjBZU4zPMLgko3_oYDV0d6Fu0lbNmdLOOU6kYjFucJM0na1RBwBFHeY_rFvuitDHPVcBO7-MsfqDmuuxbTGRaMecXG6pm9qB2oBkfDd-B3oGdGO2QpyBQiDEpzJfFtqlECFMck9hwUfzH3cc_8dd6AKK3fNlGU6AcNzk7xXm0tI1Pr8NLeNoO9h2i13HkpzlEqFw3DfW6Z153j_gGNe0HLO35Zm8L0G5_j2B71YMZJoepm6oo5aCsRX6PEDs7spH4uEUQ7M24m2ndpXRb8NhVsG5ZhxPKh9fini9e4Oh5t1NzQ7n-xlOd6etDK9puWAKlzBGYBTda1UR6be3yfojsM1nkZXmAR-f3y5DtzAOZbJzAegxPG1r2AEkuT6ebt18YS0MDM_ilW-O2z6dVfvuMFE_m9H7H907iopTtJM2tExbXAsZ9tVeCUgJ4uTdwgYz9LZ-Q1teWFwbrKcbi0-YsW5SWc8vo3P8flTU1_BSBso7CQBpDwC1WlQKg47kIwqeUEDyJdCSHCtVkMA3gIL9PsmAmmEV4clLZW8FXM2V4eG4fyCMqkvVRWpzEfEgB-dkMBFAuAF09oqgWSv_WYYmEecGUM-6iVnZViVEACj8sF_39pHD6YEcUzYIXudD1Sh_WWPivAuw0k6mHwqkafR8I3-70RiEEevKc0DZGvntOvaF29BHbPialQdWCYMHYrVYqiX_9trdNfkGe_TC1OVleEj7zgnJmaRe-PryOBKJ-DDB0uUXbtdWFC9j5MPgs3yXHs9cIxlOHgtSefatNByZYzDJmKjpwf9nnkJFZm4oD0Q1LPTZUX9gkC9Y1eSimwauF4SqBHB6wp7KZiNWbVcsSqbl8xQZW2O-VKyQsFiHHdMeYFDNBm2W5R-UuX2pqpynXCaJ6M-f1HfhXrCzUcl9rI575z6P7GVhApBxAHVpnhJkItl_lAmN-wFDz_j5iDbKooC8GHHyk1S6Gldmcs4H2xOuFajVxbY8LLuaRhw7lz1WOTUHc_xG5yZQufFKIDtz3RreOftZ246tOf0kG252cpMx0YL7Hz-YxNk9Rz4D7TplYdvW8IacfIXt0bZYjoceLZ7TYiLJushSRUHqlWSQf2NY_S05idqoI8XvxP4vgVh_D2HSo3eO_pRSHfX8bVfzohABFEFOCpcYDJHtlV-B78iR-6hAAZF4nRpvJA7UjEZO7-QOkfpwbNr1TRP18BqfM7KjYNkN7iz3tJkPfss84j5BjA0czFJ8dV2mMrsVGoKhdFPAf5k7iIfFq_irUSBEIUrcxUvKN8ValzIhCQ6skDBp_orgOyxyJhSsYGgY7nuAQHb3kmo_QZkBQxz1KFa59COGRQ9FLnQEp8XmEMC2xlE6jLS-hiyk14S7w0GxKcSzjdvdLAhhkk2_40zxt8MXG8RErRuusMvMtIx6n9knHyPZ6